<p>
<note n="0894007" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0894007">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】，【原】麗本</note>
<note n="0894008" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0894008">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0894009" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0894009">三【大】，唐三【宋】【元】【明】</note>
